original: ** We're stranded in Nowhere... **
zh_trans: **我们被困在了一个无名之地...**

original: ** Wait until something happens! **
zh_trans: **再等一会！**

original: ** What journey will this binary+1 entscheidungsproblem lead us to..? **
zh_trans: **这个二进制+1 判定问题将带领我们踏上怎样的旅程？**

original: ** Behind this door may await the Beast of All Cunning Hallways... **
zh_trans: **在这扇门后面，狡诈的走廊之兽或许在等着我们...**

original: ** Cunning Hallways shall be -of course- those that contain Barely Anything -or was it everything-. **
zh_trans: ** 这些狡诈的走廊几乎没有任何东西 - 或者说包含了一切？ **

original: ** Wait here! A wise word might come from HIGH **
zh_trans: **在此稍等！High也许会传来提示**

original: ** Some time has passed and yet no words came... May HIGH have lied? **
zh_trans: ** 一段时间过后，还是没有任何消息... 难道High撒谎了? **

original: ** It opened but... no word was read or heard... Or was it that we couldn't understand? **
zh_trans: ** 门开了……但是，没有任何有效信息……亦或是，我们根本无法理解? **

original: ** On this little pool of doubt we must stand for long enough to understand... **
zh_trans: ** 在这片小小的困惑之池上，我们必须站立足够长的时间以便理解。... **

original: ** RESIST! Think and the paradox will come at last! **
zh_trans: ** 坚持住! 思考与悖论将至! **

original: ** The columnvator is warming up - going up to the puffy clouds requires lots of energy! **
zh_trans: ** 升降机正在预热——上升到云层需要大量的能量! **

original: ** RESIST! Time is long as to make this little time step nothing - if at all... **
zh_trans: ** 守住! 人生如此漫长，这点时间可以忽略不计——如果真的可以的话... **

original: ** It stopped for some reason! **
zh_trans: ** 因为一些原因停下来了! **

original: ** Perhaps this conveniently placed valve will unlock the reason why? **
zh_trans: ** 或许这个能轻易放置的阀门能解释原因 **

original: ** The entrance to the port of all paradoxes will open soon... **
zh_trans: ** 悖论之门很快开启... **

original: ** We've opened the valve and the reason has been revealed... **
zh_trans: ** 我们打开了阀门，原因已昭然若揭... **

original: ** It just says 'to have a reason for the valve to be - aesthetics aside'... **
zh_trans: ** 只能说，“阀门存在即合理——美学除外”... **

original: ** Although small all paradoxes fit in -a paradox told me- because they're quite slim... **
zh_trans: **一个悖论告诉我：虽然很小，但所有的悖论都能适应。因为他们非常狭长... **

original: ** Well done! Now we can get out of this mess of a place and start being by our own beingness! **
zh_trans: ** 干得漂亮！现在我们可以离开这个乱七八糟的地方恢复我们本来的生活了！ **

original: ** RESIST! The flying floaty matter will take a bit of time to get us out... **
zh_trans: ** 守住! 飞板会花一点时间带我们走... **

original: ** THE RIDE NEVER ENDS! **
zh_trans: ** 旅程永无止境! **
